\   (A P) = Q * A
\
\ ******************************************************************************

                        \ --- Mod: Code removed for Elite-A: ------------------>

\.MUT2
\
\LDX XX+1               \ Set S = XX+1
\STX S
\
\                       \ Fall through into MUT1 to do the following:
